### 1. అన్ని trains
GET http://localhost:5000/trains

### 2. Search (అన్నీ ఇందులోనే!)
GET http://localhost:3000/trains/search?day=mon


### 3. Train Number తో
GET http://localhost:3000/trains/search?trainnumber=12001

### 4. Update
PUT http://localhost:3000/trains/number/:trainNumber

### 5. Delete
DELETE http://localhost:3000/trains/:id 

###  register
